<style>
  .tech-features {
    background-color: #000; /* Fundo Preto */
    color: #fff;
    padding: 60px 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #222;
  }

  .tech-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 30px;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .tech-item {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 250px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  /* Círculo neon em volta do ícone */
  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #D4AF37; /* Borda Rosa */
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.3); /* Brilho Neon */
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .tech-item:hover .icon-wrapper {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    background-color: rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.1);
  }

  .tech-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    fill: #D4AF37; /* Ícone Rosa */
  }

  .tech-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tech-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #ccc;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 250px;
  }
</style>

<div class="tech-features">
  <div class="tech-container">
    
    <div class="tech-item">
      <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <svg class="tech-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M20.57 14.86L22 13.43L20.57 12L17 15.57L8.43 7L12 3.43L10.57 2L9.14 3.43L7.71 2L5.57 4.14L4.14 2.71L2.71 4.14L4.14 5.57L2 7.71L3.43 9.14L2 10.57L3.43 12L7 8.43L15.57 17L12 20.57L13.43 22L14.86 20.57L16.29 22L18.43 19.86L19.86 21.29L21.29 19.86L19.86 18.43L22 16.29L20.57 14.86Z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tech-title">Alta Compressão</h3>
      <p class="tech-desc">Modela a cintura e o corpo com conforto absoluto durante o treino pesado.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-item">
      <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <svg class="tech-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tech-title">Zero Transparência</h3>
      <p class="tech-desc">Tecnologia Blackout. Segurança total no agachamento sem mostrar nada.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-item">
      <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <svg class="tech-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M19.46 11l-3.45-6.13.62-.36L15.3 4l-.6.34 1.35 2.4-5.2-3V1.5h-.7v2.24l-5.2 3 1.35-2.4-.6-.34-1.33.51.62.36L1.64 11H4v1H1.64l3.45 6.13-.62.36 1.33.51.6-.34-1.35-2.4 5.2 3v2.24h.7v-2.24l5.2-3-1.35 2.4.6.34 1.33-.51-.62-.36L19.46 12h-2.36v-1h2.36zM12 13.5c-.83 0-1.5-.67-1.5-1.5s.67-1.5 1.5-1.5 1.5.67 1.5 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5 1.5z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="tech-title">Tecnologia Dry</h3>
      <p class="tech-desc">Não retém suor. Sua pele seca e fresca por muito mais tempo.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

